-----------------------------------------
16. ONE-LINE INTERVIEW ANSWER
-----------------------------------------
std::unordered_map is a hash table-based associative container that stores key-value pairs with average O(1) lookup, insertion, and deletion, but does not maintain any ordering of keys.
